dict.string: LinkTunes is a tweak which let you download any mp3 directly from iTunesStore searching on all the best mp3 search engine. LinkTunes and HackYouriPhone doesn't host any file and the content that you see is not stored on our servers. LinkTunes acts as a reference only to other independent third-party Web sites.
